---
import Layout from "~/ui/components/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Pricing - TremTec">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-base-content mb-6">
        Flexible Engineering. Built for Your Pace.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-base-content/70 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We scale our team to match your project, timeline, and budget. No fixed roles. No long-term commitments. 
        Just the right people, the right time.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three Core Services -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
      <!-- Fractional CTO -->
      <div class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-primary text-xl">🔍</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-base-content mb-3">Fractional CTO</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
          Uncover where you're actually slow. Get a clear velocity roadmap.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded p-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold mb-2">Investment</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-base-content">$5K–$15K</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-1">1–2 weeks</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ SDLC deep dive
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ Bottleneck identification
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ Recommended roadmap
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-base-content/60 mb-4">
          <strong>Team:</strong> 1 Senior Engineer (lead) + optional specialists
        </p>

        <a href="#contact" class="text-primary font-semibold hover:text-primary/80 transition">
          Schedule a call →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Implementation -->
      <div class="bg-base-100 border-2 border-primary rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 left-8 bg-primary text-base-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">
          MOST POPULAR
        </div>
        
        <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-primary text-xl">⚙️</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-base-content mb-3">Implementation</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
          Build reproducible SDLCs with AI. Your team learns sustainable patterns.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded p-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold mb-2">Investment</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-base-content">$25K–$75K</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-1">4–8 weeks</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ Dedicated engineering squad
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ Full SDLC setup + AI integration
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ Knowledge transfer (your team learns)
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ Independent after engagement
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-base-content/60 mb-4">
          <strong>Team:</strong> 1 Lead + 1–3 Engineers (scales with scope)
        </p>

        <a href="#contact" class="text-primary font-semibold hover:text-primary/80 transition">
          Get a quote →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Mentoring -->
      <div class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-primary text-xl">🎓</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-base-content mb-3">Mentoring</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
          Ongoing coaching for AI mastery and sustainable velocity.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded p-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold mb-2">Investment</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-base-content">$5K–$8K/mo</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-1">Month-to-month</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ Monthly strategy sessions
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ On-demand technical guidance
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            ✓ Pattern refinement & optimization
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-base-content/60 mb-4">
          <strong>Team:</strong> 1 Senior Engineer (flexible hours)
        </p>

        <a href="#contact" class="text-primary font-semibold hover:text-primary/80 transition">
          Learn more →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison Banner -->
  <section class="bg-base-200 px-6 py-16 border-t border-base-300">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-base-content mb-8 text-center">
        Why Teams Choose TremTec
      </h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">40%</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">Average velocity gain in first month</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">0</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">Monthly retainers after engagement</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">1 week</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">Average ramp-up for new hires</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">100%</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">Knowledge ownership by your team</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Flexibility Section -->
  <section class="bg-base-200 px-6 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-center text-base-content">
        Resources That Flex With You
      </h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-base-content">Team Composition</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
            We don't force a standard "squad." Depending on your project, we might allocate:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>Full-stack engineers</strong> for end-to-end features</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>Architects</strong> for complex system design</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>DevOps/Infrastructure</strong> for deployment & scaling</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>AI specialists</strong> for LLM integration</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>Product coaches</strong> for process design</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-base-content">Engagement Models</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
            Choose what fits your constraints:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>Embedded</strong> — Squad works in your office/timezone</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>Remote</strong> — Async-first, flexible async overlap</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>Hybrid</strong> — Key people co-located, rest remote</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>Part-time</strong> — We flex hours based on your needs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3">→</span>
              <span><strong>Full-time</strong> — Dedicated squad for sprint duration</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Drivers -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-base-content mb-12 text-center">
      What Shapes Your Investment
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div class="bg-base-200 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Scope</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
          What are we building?
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-base-content/70">
          <li>• Single feature vs. full SDLC overhaul</li>
          <li>• Team size (5 engineers vs. 50)</li>
          <li>• Technical complexity (legacy code vs. greenfield)</li>
          <li>• Integration requirements</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-200 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Timeline</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
          How fast do you need results?
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-base-content/70">
          <li>• 4-week sprint vs. 12-week program</li>
          <li>• Intensity (half-time vs. full-time)</li>
          <li>• Ramp-up and knowledge transfer overlap</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-200 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Team Composition</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
          Who do you need?
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-base-content/70">
          <li>• Senior architect vs. full-stack team</li>
          <li>• Specialized expertise (DevOps, AI, etc.)</li>
          <li>• Seniority levels</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-base-200 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-base-content mb-4">Support Model</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6">
          What happens after?
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-base-content/70">
          <li>• Standalone engagement vs. + mentoring</li>
          <li>• Hand-off readiness (docs, training)</li>
          <li>• Ongoing optimization retainer</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-base-200 px-6 py-20" id="contact">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-base-content">
        Let's Talk About Your Project
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Every project is different. We'll listen to your constraints, scope, and timeline—then propose a flexible staffing model that actually fits.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="mailto:hello@tremtec.com?subject=Inquiry%20about%20services" 
            class="btn btn-primary font-bold">
          Book a 30-min call
        </a>
        <a href="#" 
            class="btn btn-outline">
          See case studies
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60 mt-6">
        Or email <strong>hello@tremtec.com</strong> with your project details.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="bg-base-200 px-6 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-base-content mb-12 text-center">
        Frequently Asked
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <details class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-base-content flex items-center justify-between">
            Is this replacing our team?
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition">→</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4">
            No. We teach your team to master modern practices. The goal is independence—after our engagement, you own the process. We're not a permanent dependency.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-base-content flex items-center justify-between">
            Can we scale the team up or down mid-project?
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition">→</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4">
            Yes. We adjust staffing based on actual needs. If you discover scope changes or hit a roadblock, we flex. There's no penalty for rightsizing.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-base-content flex items-center justify-between">
            What if we need ongoing support?
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition">→</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4">
            Add our Mentoring tier ($5K–$8K/month). Your lead engineer stays involved for strategy, reviews, and pattern refinement. Very different from a fractional CTO retainer—this is coaching, not substitution.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-base-content flex items-center justify-between">
            Do you work remote?
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition">→</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4">
            Yes. Full remote, embedded, hybrid—whatever works for you. We design engagement models around your constraints, not ours.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-base-content flex items-center justify-between">
            What's included in knowledge transfer?
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition">→</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4">
            Documentation of patterns, code walkthroughs, team training sessions, and overlap time with your engineers. You'll have ownership + understanding by the end, not just handed-off code.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-base-100 border border-base-300 rounded-lg p-6 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition group">
          <summary class="font-bold text-base-content flex items-center justify-between">
            How is this different from hiring a Fractional CTO?
            <span class="group-open:rotate-180 transition">→</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4">
            Fractional CTOs ($5K–$10K/month) lead your tech indefinitely. You stay dependent. TremTec Implementation ($25K–$75K upfront, 4–8 weeks) teaches your team sustainable practices, then you operate independently. If you want ongoing support, add Mentoring—but your team is steering, not us.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
